    <body>
      <div type="letter">
        <head>
          <title>21 June 1731. – [Letter from <persName
              key="p0220"
              ref="3246c251-a0fd-44f4-b6fd-3a306dd0c117">the Russian Envoy Extraordinary to the
            Ottoman Porte, Prince Ivan Andreevich Shcherbatov,]</persName> to [the German merchant,]
            Herman Meyer, written in <placeName key="g0001">Moscow</placeName> on June 21, 1731</title>
          <note>
            <bibl>NLR Mss, fond Erm., no. 123-4, f. 135v–136. Copy of English original.</bibl>
          </note>
        </head>
        <p />
        <pb n="f. 135v" />
        <p>В <placeName key="g0001">Москве</placeName> от 21го июня 1731 году к <persName
            key="p0329">Герману Меэру</persName> писано</p>
        <p>I send to you an opened Letter to <persName
            key="p0330"
            ref="3293fc58-87c8-446c-99af-c5f7dcc863a4">mr. Ertman</persName> Resident in <placeName
            key="g0014">Dantzig</placeName>, by which you may see </p>
        <pb n="f. 136" />
        <p> my Desire that you would be so kind as to encharge some of your Correspondent in <placeName
            key="g0014">Dantzig</placeName> to reçieve from <persName
            key="p0330"
            ref="3293fc58-87c8-446c-99af-c5f7dcc863a4">mr: Ertman</persName> a Poste Calashe that I
          Left in his house, or money for the same as many as he’ll give to your Correspondent. In
          the mean time I doe beseeche you to rite [sic!] to the said your Correspondent that he
          should send the above mentioned Calashe by the first ship to <placeName key="g0015">Riga</placeName>
          to some of your acquaintance, and as soon shall arrive there to Let me know of the same,
          in doing which you'll oblige etc.</p>
        <p>P.S. I doe answer for the Expences that you shall spend for the Ports of the Letters, and
          for the Carriage of the said Calashe.</p>
        <noteGrp>
          <note>Also see:</note>
          <note>ru_nlrmss_erm_123-4_0037</note>
        </noteGrp>
      </div>
